{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T08:56:48.309Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The pricing model for "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude Managed Agents"},{"type":"text","text":" is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"hybrid of standard Claude API token costs plus a runtime fee for active session time"},{"type":"text","text":", with active runtime charged at "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"$0.08 per session-hour"},{"type":"text","text":". This means an agent that runs continuously 24/7 costs roughly "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"$58/month"},{"type":"text","text":" in instance fees alone ($0.08/hour × 24 hours × 30 days ≈ $57.60), plus whatever you pay for Claude tokens consumed during that time."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Managed Agents charges two types of costs:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Token costs"},{"type":"text","text":": Standard Claude API rates for prompt and completion tokens (same as the regular API).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Instance (runtime) costs"},{"type":"text","text":": $0.08 per hour of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"active session runtime"},{"type":"text","text":" while the agent is executing in the sandbox."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The \"~$58/month per 24/7 agent\" figure comes purely from the instance cost:\n- $0.08/hour × 24 hours/day × 30 days ≈ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"$57.60/month"},{"type":"text","text":".\n- This is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"minimum"},{"type":"text","text":" for a continuously running agent, regardless of token usage."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If the agent also consumes tokens (e.g., 100k input tokens + 50k output tokens per month at typical Claude rates), you add those token costs on top of the $58 base."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The runtime fee reflects that Managed Agents is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"hosted long-running infrastructure"},{"type":"text","text":", not just a chat API. You're paying for:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cloud sandboxes"},{"type":"text","text":": Secure execution environments with pre-installed packages and network access.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Autonomous agent loop"},{"type":"text","text":": The platform handles tool execution, context management, and error recovery.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"State persistence"},{"type":"text","text":": Conversation history, filesystem state, and outputs are stored server-side."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For production workloads, this means:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Short tasks"},{"type":"text","text":": You pay mostly for tokens; runtime is negligible.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long-running tasks"},{"type":"text","text":": You pay significantly for active runtime, which can be the dominant cost.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"24/7 agents"},{"type":"text","text":": Runtime fees become around $58/month per agent, plus token costs."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of it as:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Token costs"},{"type":"text","text":" = \"brain costs\" (how much Claude thinks).\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Instance costs"},{"type":"text","text":" = \"body costs\" (how long the agent body is actively running in the sandbox)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The $58/month figure is the cost of keeping the agent's \"body\" active 24/7, regardless of how much it thinks."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When this model applies"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This pricing is best for workloads that need:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Long-running execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Tasks that run for minutes or hours with multiple tool calls.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cloud infrastructure"},{"type":"text","text":": Secure sandboxes with pre-installed packages and network access.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stateful sessions"},{"type":"text","text":": Persistent filesystems and conversation history across interactions.\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Minimal infrastructure"},{"type":"text","text":": No need to build your own agent loop, sandbox, or tool execution layer."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"short, bursty tasks"},{"type":"text","text":", token costs dominate. For "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"continuous agents"},{"type":"text","text":", runtime fees dominate."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Comparison with alternatives"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Platform"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pricing model"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Managed Agents"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token costs + $0.08/hour active runtime"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Long-running, stateful agents"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Regular Claude API"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token costs only"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Short, bursty prompts"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Self-hosted"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Your infrastructure costs + tokens"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Compliance, custom orchestration"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Managed Agents is more expensive per hour than just paying for tokens, because you're also paying for the managed infrastructure. But you save the 3–6 months of engineering time to build your own sandbox, agent loop, and state management."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Practical examples"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 1: Short task (10 minutes)"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Runtime: 10 minutes = 0.17 hours."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Instance cost: $0.08 × 0.17 ≈ $0.01."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token cost: 50k input + 20k output tokens ≈ $1–$3 (depending on model)."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Total"},{"type":"text","text":": ~$1–$3 (token cost dominates)."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 2: Long-running task (5 hours)"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Runtime: 5 hours."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Instance cost: $0.08 × 5 = $0.40."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token cost: 200k input + 100k output tokens ≈ $5–$15."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Total"},{"type":"text","text":": ~$5–$15 (token cost still dominates, but runtime is noticeable)."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 3: 24/7 agent (30 days)"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Runtime: 24 × 30 = 720 hours."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Instance cost: $0.08 × 720 ≈ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"$57.60/month"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Token cost: 1M input + 500k output tokens ≈ $30–$90 (depending on model)."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Total"},{"type":"text","text":": ~$90–$150/month (runtime cost is ~$58, plus tokens)."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is where the \"$58/month per 24/7 agent\" figure comes from: the runtime cost for a continuously running agent."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cost optimization strategies"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Pause when idle"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If the agent is \"waiting\" but not actively executing tools, you can "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"pause the session"},{"type":"text","text":" to stop charging runtime. When you resume, the agent continues from the same state."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. Use cheaper models for simple tasks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For lightweight agent work, use "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude Haiku"},{"type":"text","text":" instead of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sonnet"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Opus"},{"type":"text","text":" to reduce token costs. Runtime costs are the same regardless of model."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Limit tool calls"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each tool call usually triggers a model request. Reducing unnecessary tool calls reduces token usage."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. Batch work"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Instead of spreading work across many small sessions, batch tasks into fewer, longer sessions to reduce overhead."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. Consider self-hosted for 24/7"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need many 24/7 agents, self-hosted sandboxes might be cheaper at scale, but you pay for orchestration engineering time."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Managed Agents charges "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"standard token rates + $0.08 per active session-hour"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"24/7 agent costs ~$58/month"},{"type":"text","text":" in runtime fees alone ($0.08 × 24 × 30)."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Token costs"},{"type":"text","text":" are the same as the regular Claude API; "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"runtime fees"},{"type":"text","text":" are the additional Managed Agents cost."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"short tasks"},{"type":"text","text":", token costs dominate. For "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"continuous agents"},{"type":"text","text":", runtime fees dominate."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The model is designed for "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"long-running, stateful agents"},{"type":"text","text":" where you don't want to build your own infrastructure."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
